  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built for people who love board games, All On Board! brings game nights back to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The laughter, the rivalry, the quiet focus before a decisive roll, it’s all here in VR. Gather around a virtual table that feels real, no matter how far apart you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All On Board! is a tool that lets you enjoy digital versions of the tabletop games you love. The library includes free classics and reknowned licensed titles sold separately as DLC (DLC purchase is required only to host, you can join any game with just the base app).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game is adapted with care and respect for what makes it special. Every shuffle, move, and chaotic moment shared among friends is brought to life in virtual space. This isn’t about replacing the table. It’s about expanding it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lifelike VR tabletop experience with realistic physics and intuitive controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only the host buys the licensed title; others join with the base app</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growing library of licensed favorites and free classics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-platform and multi-language support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo, co-op, or competitive sessions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learning Hub in every game to help you learn fast</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save and resume anytime</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/de68a7779e644bb946cb2d45386eddd0.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/de68a7779e644bb946cb2d45386eddd0.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/de68a7779e644bb946cb2d45386eddd0.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic games included: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Checkers, Go, Chess, and Parchisi.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >French deck card games.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find other players in our Discord or Telegram and start a session (no AI opponents yet).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All On Board! is made by an independent studio that loves board games as much as you do. It’s built on passion, constant updates, and a growing lineup of great titles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/caf267b11ed2b2cfe4c69593f7dca5fe.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/caf267b11ed2b2cfe4c69593f7dca5fe.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/caf267b11ed2b2cfe4c69593f7dca5fe.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built for people who love board games, All On Board! brings game nights back to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The laughter, the rivalry, the quiet focus before a decisive roll, it’s all here in VR. Gather around a virtual table that feels real, no matter how far apart you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All On Board! is a tool that lets you enjoy digital versions of the tabletop games you love. The library includes free classics and reknowned licensed titles sold separately as DLC (DLC purchase is required only to host, you can join any game with just the base app).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game is adapted with care and respect for what makes it special. Every shuffle, move, and chaotic moment shared among friends is brought to life in virtual space. This isn’t about replacing the table. It’s about expanding it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lifelike VR tabletop experience with realistic physics and intuitive controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only the host buys the licensed title; others join with the base app</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growing library of licensed favorites and free classics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-platform and multi-language support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo, co-op, or competitive sessions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learning Hub in every game to help you learn fast</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save and resume anytime</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/de68a7779e644bb946cb2d45386eddd0.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/de68a7779e644bb946cb2d45386eddd0.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/de68a7779e644bb946cb2d45386eddd0.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic games included: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Checkers, Go, Chess, and Parchisi.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >French deck card games.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find other players in our Discord or Telegram and start a session (no AI opponents yet).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All On Board! is made by an independent studio that loves board games as much as you do. It’s built on passion, constant updates, and a growing lineup of great titles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/caf267b11ed2b2cfe4c69593f7dca5fe.poster.avif?t=1774371138\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/caf267b11ed2b2cfe4c69593f7dca5fe.webm?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192970/extras/caf267b11ed2b2cfe4c69593f7dca5fe.mp4?t=1774371138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
